    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>RETRO-STYLE ACTION RPG ADVENTURE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > The curious young Princess has always looked for the chance to explore the world beyond the castle. Her most recent outing has left her very ill, but with the arrival of an antidote, and the king leaving town, she just can't wait to attempt yet another escape...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>NO CASUAL GAMING</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Traverse a vast non-linear kingdom of endless secrets, hostile creatures, and unfair traps.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover bountiful weapons, items and gear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Level up as you fight off common adversaries in button-mashing action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take down malevolent guardians in turn-based battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get good. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1855240/extras/b4c59ee8a1729beaa7224a4a1f9d5a12.webp?t=1764401121\" width=16 height=16 /></span></p>",
